WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.776
March twenty twenty-six Monthly Review. March was a convergence month.

00:00:04.776 --> 00:00:09.553
Katelyn's eight-day visit, the Anthropic court victory, condo renovation milestones,

00:00:09.553 --> 00:00:14.329
and the sudden emergence of The Keeping House writing streak

00:00:14.329 --> 00:00:19.106
all collided into the densest month of the year so

00:00:19.106 --> 00:00:23.882
far. Patterns. Relationship resets through presence. The four-week pattern of

00:00:23.882 --> 00:00:28.659
tension and distance dissolved during Katelyn's visit from March fourteenth

00:00:28.659 --> 00:00:33.435
through the twenty-second. Hermann wine weekend, then Jeff City midweek

00:00:33.435 --> 00:00:38.212
with friends, then Saint Charles with family. Post-visit texting was

00:00:38.212 --> 00:00:42.988
warm and consistent. But the underlying geographic mismatch remains structural,

00:00:42.988 --> 00:00:47.765
not relational. Intensive visits reset the emotional baseline. They don't

00:00:47.765 --> 00:00:52.541
resolve the distance question. Work as invisible infrastructure. Legislative session

00:00:52.541 --> 00:00:57.318
crunch ran underneath everything. H-B twenty-two seventy-three, S-B eight eighty-eight

00:00:57.318 --> 00:01:02.094
staffing, Bill Review Training, B-Rs to the Governor's Office delivered

00:01:02.094 --> 00:01:06.871
March twenty-sixth. Karen's retirement on April first triggers hiring projects.

00:01:06.871 --> 00:01:11.647
Work rarely dominates the daily notes, but it's always there.

00:01:11.647 --> 00:01:16.424
The constant baseline that career decisions lurk beneath. Condo project

00:01:16.424 --> 00:01:21.200
momentum. The renovation tracked weekly. Shower tile finale with Dad

00:01:21.200 --> 00:01:25.977
March seventh and eighth. Bathroom finishing touches and Lowe's runs

00:01:25.977 --> 00:01:30.753
mid-March. Flooring quotes. Then carpet install with Ben on March

00:01:30.753 --> 00:01:35.530
thirty-first. The home is becoming a shared family project. Dad

00:01:35.530 --> 00:01:40.306
on tile, Ben on carpet, Maggie getting curious about Claude.

00:01:40.306 --> 00:01:45.083
The integration theme manifesting through the physical space. Reading diet,

00:01:45.083 --> 00:01:49.859
intentionally skewed. Seventy-seven percent A-I and tech, explicitly flagged for

00:01:49.859 --> 00:01:54.636
diversity improvement. Deep Readwise sessions on A-I governance. Helen Toner,

00:01:54.636 --> 00:01:59.412
Jack Clark, Senate guardrails. This isn't accidental. It reflects the

00:01:59.412 --> 00:02:04.189
career question and Anthropic tracking. Ezra Klein's cognitive surrender piece

00:02:04.189 --> 00:02:08.965
on March twenty-ninth hit the meta-level. The vault itself is

00:02:08.965 --> 00:02:13.742
an example of reshaping yourself to be legible to A-I.

00:02:13.742 --> 00:02:18.518
Iran war as ambient backdrop. Every briefing references it, from

00:02:18.518 --> 00:02:23.295
Day fifteen through Day thirty-one. But it never breaks through

00:02:23.295 --> 00:02:28.071
to personal urgency. Oil tracked at one-sixteen peak. Geopolitics noted,

00:02:28.071 --> 00:02:32.848
but no personal action or anxiety. An ambient crisis that

00:02:32.848 --> 00:02:37.624
shapes the world without demanding immediate response. Tensions. The geography-career-relationship

00:02:37.624 --> 00:02:42.401
triangle. This is the big one. The March twenty-ninth job

00:02:42.401 --> 00:02:47.177
research, City of Seattle Economics and Revenue Analyst as best

00:02:47.177 --> 00:02:51.954
near-term fit, is the strongest signal that the decision is

00:02:51.954 --> 00:02:56.730
pressing. But no application was submitted. Meanwhile, the Anthropic pilot

00:02:56.730 --> 00:03:01.507
deepens the state government commitment. Katelyn's July time-off needs coordination.

00:03:01.507 --> 00:03:06.283
Three vectors pulling in different directions. No resolution yet. Financial

00:03:06.283 --> 00:03:11.059
deployment, deferred. The roughly fifty-thousand dollars excess cash plus Roth

00:03:11.059 --> 00:03:15.836
max has been flagged every single daily note since March

00:03:15.836 --> 00:03:20.612
first. Ten-plus weeks overdue on March eighth. Still open at

00:03:20.612 --> 00:03:25.389
month's end. Fully deferred into April. Ray and Pam's Bora

00:03:25.389 --> 00:03:30.165
Bora email. Tracked from March first, still floating, through March

00:03:30.165 --> 00:03:34.942
twenty-second, seven weeks, write it this week or consciously drop

00:03:34.942 --> 00:03:39.718
it, to March thirty-first, now ten weeks, decision time. Appearing

00:03:39.718 --> 00:03:44.495
less frequently, suggesting conscious deprioritization. Ecobee sixty-degree automation bug. First

00:03:44.495 --> 00:03:49.271
alerted March tenth, flagged four-plus times by March thirteenth, marked

00:03:49.271 --> 00:03:54.048
complete March twenty-seventh with no actual fix noted. Probably a

00:03:54.048 --> 00:03:58.824
conscious decision to stop worrying about it rather than a

00:03:58.824 --> 00:04:03.601
resolution. Wins. Anthropic court victory, March twenty-fourth through twenty-sixth. The

00:04:03.601 --> 00:04:08.377
forty-three page preliminary injunction. Classic illegal First Amendment retaliation. Orwellian.

00:04:08.377 --> 00:04:13.154
Not tailored to stated national security concern. This was the

00:04:13.154 --> 00:04:17.930
month's biggest arc. Tracked obsessively across Dwarkesh Patel, Scott Alexander,

00:04:17.930 --> 00:04:22.707
Krugman, Alex Heath, M-I-T Tech Review. Federal agencies can resume

00:04:22.707 --> 00:04:27.483
using Claude. This validates the Anthropic thesis Jacob has been

00:04:27.483 --> 00:04:32.260
building all year. B-Rs delivered to the Governor's Office, March

00:04:32.260 --> 00:04:37.036
twenty-sixth. Multiple briefings flagged this as pressing. Corrected a sixty-five

00:04:37.036 --> 00:04:41.813
page document in one evening session. Delivered on schedule during

00:04:41.813 --> 00:04:46.589
the most intense week of the month. Fitness consistency. Gym

00:04:46.589 --> 00:04:51.366
attendance ramped from four times per week in early March

00:04:51.366 --> 00:04:56.142
to five weekdays plus weekend hikes and runs by month's

00:04:56.142 --> 00:05:00.919
end. Y-M-C-A booked five days a week, five-fifteen to seven

00:05:00.919 --> 00:05:05.695
P-M. Sleep averaging seven-and-a-half hours at ninety-eight percent plus efficiency.

00:05:05.695 --> 00:05:10.472
R-E-M consistently over two hours. Reader is the top app

00:05:10.472 --> 00:05:15.248
at two hours and ten minutes, replacing scrolling. Sustainable pattern,

00:05:15.248 --> 00:05:20.025
not a sprint. The Keeping House emerged. Chapter two, The

00:05:20.025 --> 00:05:24.801
Table, written and published as a twenty-two minute podcast episode

00:05:24.801 --> 00:05:29.578
on March thirtieth. Chapter one already complete. Characters doc updated

00:05:29.578 --> 00:05:34.354
with Callan's backstory. The outline, characters, world, and style guide

00:05:34.354 --> 00:05:39.131
were all in place. The daily execution just clicked at

00:05:39.131 --> 00:05:43.907
month's end. Publishing to podcast suggests real intent, not just

00:05:43.907 --> 00:05:48.684
experimentation. Vault architecture improvements. Daily Briefings reorganized into a dedicated

00:05:48.684 --> 00:05:53.460
folder. Weekly review rhythm restored with two consecutive weeks. Sunday

00:05:53.460 --> 00:05:58.237
check-in folder created with five reports. The infrastructure is actively

00:05:58.237 --> 00:06:03.013
improving. Relationships. Katelyn. Tension to connection. Pre-visit worry gave way

00:06:03.013 --> 00:06:07.790
to eight dense days together. Multiple settings. Hermann wine country.

00:06:07.790 --> 00:06:12.566
Jeff City with friends, bingo at Last Flight. Saint Charles

00:06:12.566 --> 00:06:17.342
with the Brooke family. Post-visit warmth sustained through month's end.

00:06:17.342 --> 00:06:22.119
She passed her B-C-P-P exam March twelfth. Hylo Athletics running

00:06:22.119 --> 00:06:26.895
shoes acquired for Tacoma City Half Marathon training on May

00:06:26.895 --> 00:06:31.672
third. Crow cult doctrine developing via bird feeder. Outstanding item:

00:06:31.672 --> 00:06:36.448
July time-off coordination. Ben. Collaborative energy. Settled the Friday dinner

00:06:36.448 --> 00:06:41.225
split at about two-thirty-seven, arriving for carpet install March thirty-first,

00:06:41.225 --> 00:06:46.001
coordinating Dad's birthday logistics. Maggie getting interested in Claude. The

00:06:46.001 --> 00:06:50.778
sibling relationship is deepening through shared condo work. Dad. Practical

00:06:50.778 --> 00:06:55.554
partnership. Tile weekend finale March seventh and eighth. Strong at

00:06:55.554 --> 00:07:00.331
the broken places. Lowe's receipts flowing. Dinner together. The father-son

00:07:00.331 --> 00:07:05.107
dynamic is expressed through doing, not talking. Friends. Thursday April

00:07:05.107 --> 00:07:09.884
second dinner with Alex, Chris, and Dustin becomes the reconnection

00:07:09.884 --> 00:07:14.660
point. Dustin going to Europe May eighth through the twenty-first,

00:07:14.660 --> 00:07:19.437
first time leaving the U-S. Alex sending Apple rankings at

00:07:19.437 --> 00:07:24.213
eleven P-M. Chris sharing small-town radio memes. The group is

00:07:24.213 --> 00:07:28.990
diverse, distributed, and consistent. Career. Claude pilot approved and advancing.

00:07:28.990 --> 00:07:33.766
The pilot moved from approval to implementation discussion. March thirty-first

00:07:33.766 --> 00:07:38.543
sets up the April second triple-header. Nine A-M Anthropic pilot

00:07:38.543 --> 00:07:43.319
pitch. Two P-M Bill Review Training. Six P-M dinner with

00:07:43.319 --> 00:07:48.096
friends. The timing is extraordinary. Pitching Claude at state government

00:07:48.096 --> 00:07:52.872
the same week the court freed it from the Pentagon

00:07:52.872 --> 00:07:57.649
ban. Seattle job research, March twenty-ninth. City of Seattle Economics

00:07:57.649 --> 00:08:02.425
and Revenue Analyst identified as best near-term fit. King County

00:08:02.425 --> 00:08:07.202
Deputy Division Director at one-seventy-three to two-nineteen K as a

00:08:07.202 --> 00:08:11.978
strong three to five year target. Researched in depth, but

00:08:11.978 --> 00:08:16.755
not applied. Karen's retirement, April first. Structural change in the

00:08:16.755 --> 00:08:21.531
department. Hiring projects begin immediately. Both an operational demand and

00:08:21.531 --> 00:08:26.308
an opportunity. Creative Work. Five chapters in five days would

00:08:26.308 --> 00:08:31.084
happen April first through fifth, but the velocity started building

00:08:31.084 --> 00:08:35.861
in late March. Chapter two, The Table, published March thirtieth

00:08:35.861 --> 00:08:40.637
with a British female voice. P-O-V Callan Marsh. First communal

00:08:40.637 --> 00:08:45.414
meal scene. Lena commanding the kitchen. Noor deflating Fen. Callan's

00:08:45.414 --> 00:08:50.190
admission: I ran out of reasons to say no. The

00:08:50.190 --> 00:08:54.967
writing project didn't build gradually. It emerged fully formed. Outline,

00:08:54.967 --> 00:08:59.743
characters, world, style guide, podcast distribution, all ready before the

00:08:59.743 --> 00:09:04.520
execution phase started. This is a pattern worth noting for

00:09:04.520 --> 00:09:09.296
future creative work. Preparation is invisible until it isn't. Health

00:09:09.296 --> 00:09:14.072
and Fitness. Sleep averaging seven-and-a-half hours at ninety-eight percent plus

00:09:14.072 --> 00:09:18.849
efficiency. R-E-M consistently over two hours. Nine P-M wind-down routine

00:09:18.849 --> 00:09:23.625
established. Screens off, yoga, meditation, journaling, reading, melatonin at nine-thirty.

00:09:23.625 --> 00:09:28.402
Y-M-C-A attendance five days a week by month's end. Saturday

00:09:28.402 --> 00:09:33.178
hikes, Sunday run-and-lift sessions. Lunchtime walks becoming regular. This is

00:09:33.178 --> 00:09:37.955
the strongest fitness month since the streak began. Glucose control

00:09:37.955 --> 00:09:42.731
excellent. Mean ninety-nine point seven milligrams per deciliter, ninety-eight point

00:09:42.731 --> 00:09:47.508
eight percent time-in-range on Dexcom Stelo C-G-M. No nutritional issues

00:09:47.508 --> 00:09:52.284
flagged. Emerging Themes for April. April second as convergence point.

00:09:52.284 --> 00:09:57.061
Claude pilot discussion plus government appeal deadline plus friend dinner.

00:09:57.061 --> 00:10:01.837
Career, Anthropic alignment, and social life crossing on the same

00:10:01.837 --> 00:10:06.614
day. Geography decision becoming urgent. Seattle job postings researched but

00:10:06.614 --> 00:10:11.390
not applied. Katelyn's visit reinforced the relationship. Anthropic pilot deepens

00:10:11.390 --> 00:10:16.167
the Jeff City commitment. Something has to give. Or not.

00:10:16.167 --> 00:10:20.943
But the tension is sharpening. Writing velocity. If the Keeping

00:10:20.943 --> 00:10:25.720
House streak continues, and it did, five chapters by April

00:10:25.720 --> 00:10:30.496
third, April reveals the creative project as a major time

00:10:30.496 --> 00:10:35.273
commitment. The question: can Jacob sustain writing plus work plus

00:10:35.273 --> 00:10:40.049
fitness plus relationship maintenance simultaneously? Financial deployment still deferred. Twelve-plus

00:10:40.049 --> 00:10:44.826
weeks and counting. This doesn't go away by ignoring it.

00:10:44.826 --> 00:10:49.602
Condo entering execution phase. Tile done, bathroom done, carpet done.

00:10:49.602 --> 00:10:54.379
Flooring next. The renovation frees mental bandwidth as it nears

00:10:54.379 --> 00:10:59.155
completion. Key Insight. Weekly reviews are more valuable than daily

00:10:59.155 --> 00:11:03.932
notes. Only thirteen daily notes in thirty-one days, but two

00:11:03.932 --> 00:11:08.708
comprehensive weekly reviews that reveal patterns invisible in the sparse

00:11:08.708 --> 00:11:13.485
daily entries. The ratio suggests daily capture is episodic while

00:11:13.485 --> 00:11:18.261
weekly synthesis is where real thinking happens. Protect the weekly

00:11:18.261 --> 00:11:22.560
review habit. It's where the vault earns its keep.
